Package: binaryRL
Version: 0.7.9
Title: Reinforcement Learning Tools for Two-Alternative Forced Choice Tasks
Description:
  Tools for building reinforcement learning models in Two-Alternative
  Forced Choice tasks, commonly used in psychological research.
  Supports model definition using simple if-else statements, and includes
  functions for model construction, fitting, and parameter recovery.
